    "title": "About me",
    "description": "Hello, I'm Abdul Hamid, an experienced Senior Full Stack Developer based in Guadalajara, Mexico. I'm always ready to take on new challenges and explore new technologies.",
    "content": "Beyond my professional commitments, which you can follow on my [LinkedIn](http://linkedin.com/in/abdulachik/) and [GitHub](https://github.com/abdul-hamid-achik), I'm an avid reader with a particular interest in psychoanalysis and authors like Jacques Lacan and Fyodor Dostoyevsky. You can find my reading list [here](https://www.goodreads.com/abdulhamidachik).\n\nI speak fluent English and Spanish, with basic knowledge of Russian and Arabic. I identify as a Lacanian atheist liberal, a perspective that informs my approach to life and work.\n\nThis website serves as a platform to share my ideas, experiences, and stories. My goal is to entertain, educate, and learn alongside my readers through a mix of technical posts, reflections on literature and philosophy, and personal narratives.\n\nIf you have any questions, want to chat, or wish to book a time to speak with me, don't hesitate to contact me at [my email](mailto:goad.00potions@icloud.com) or schedule a meeting through [Cal](https://cal.com/d/tn2bq9am4v5t9TbTF9Mr6C/30min).\n\nFeel free to explore!",
